Loading Codio, hold tight...

Sorry there seems to be a problem loading your assignment

  • check cookies are set correctly
  • clear cookies/cache (select 'all time')
  • try in a private/incognito browser (where any browser addons/extensions won't be running)
  • try a different browser that you haven't used before
  • check any local firewall/AntiVirus apps that are running (they all should have log files to show if they are blocking anything -- some have 'default' settings that they say are to protect you but can interfere a lot!
  • If you are using Safari browser it can be blocking preview cookies with their 'Intelligent Tracking Prevention 2.0', Look to disable the cookie block of the browser, refresh and try again

If you still have a problem please contact us at help@codio.com with details of the assignment and what browsers you have tried.
